Hello world! 

That's my very first NFT. 
I'm very grateful for being a part of NFT community. 
So here's what: 
That's a photo of rainbow on a waterfall Makkuntseti in a Georgia mountains. 
It was captured around 12am on a last day of 2021 — on a 31st of December.
It's a gift. 
I wish you great 2022.
